               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist; groups of lines on the incipit page of each section of the text; two initial lines of each subsection; word sälam "salutation"; elements of the punctuation signs and of the text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Each section includes the following hymns:</note>
                     <note>I-1) ኦዘመሐርከ፡ ለዕንጦንዮስ፡ ባህታዊ። ... (fol. 4va-vb)</note>
                     <note>I-2) እንበለ፡ ሕማም፡ {አምላክ፡} አመ፡ ከመ፡ ዮም። ... (fol. 13vb)</note>
                     <note>I-3) ኦዘአድኃንኮሙ፡ ለደቂቀ፡ ሕግ፡ ፫ቱ፡ ... (fol. 21vb)</note>
                     <note>I-4) ኦዘድኃንእኮ፡ ለቴዎድሮስ፡ መዋዒ። ... (fol. 30rb)</note>
                     <note>I-5) ኦዘወሀብኮ፡ እምአፈ፡ በላዒ፡ መብልዓ። ... (fols. 35vb-36ra)</note>
                     <note>I-6) ኦዘተዛለፍኮ፡ ለበለዓም፡ በፍኖቱ። ... (fol. 52vb)</note>
                     <note>I-7) ኦዘባላሕኮሙ፡ በወርኃ፡ ሚያዝያ፡ ወርኃ፡ ባልሖ።... (fol. 64ra)</note>
                     <note>I-8) ኦዘፆርከ፡ በክሳደ፡ እክል፡ አኃዜ፡ ... (fol. 65rb)</note>
                     <note>I-9) ኦዘድኃንእካ፡ እምኃጕለ፡ መብረቅ፡ ወትንታኔ። ... (fol. 75vb)</note>
                     <note>I-10) ኦዘቀተለከ፡ ሰናክሬምሃ፡ ጸዓሌ። ... (fol. 82rb)</note>
                     <note>I-11) ኦዘአጽናዕከ፡ ቍስጣንጢኖስሃ፡ ኃሣሤ። ... (fol. 89ra)</note>
                     <note>I-12) ኦዘፈወስኮ፡ ለሕዝቅያስ፡ እምደዊሁ። ... (fol. 96rb)</note>
                     <note>I-13) ኦዘኃደጎ፡ ለዘኃደገ፡ መንፈሱ። ... (fol. 105va).</note>
